sly staying updated with Digital Analytics, Tracking, Marketing Measurement, MarTech, Automation, and AI applications, including conference attendance and volunteering.', 'Experience in developing own AI agents, showcasing advanced technical and problem-solving skills which could be an asset for future automation in analytics.', 'Experience with other analytics tools like eTracker and Webtrekk demonstrates broader expertise.', 'Experience with BigQuery and SQL for data analysis and preparation.', 'Proven ability to translate business questions into data-driven solutions and decision-making processes.', 'Ability to manage external agencies and build in-house structures.', 'Experience with CRO (Conversion Rate Optimization).'], 'summary': 'The candidate is a strong match for the Digital Analytics / Web Tracking Expert role, possessing extensive hands-on experience with GA4, GTM, Looker Studio, consent management, and diverse marketing channels, along with a solid technical foundation in JavaScript and server-side tracking, though Power BI experience is not explicitly stated.'}"}
